{"tid":1609823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下你地唔好再叫黑警走","createTime":"2019-10-01T15:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T16:27:54.000Z","uid":37054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d8ab5796dacfb2144070aa076809d67e4ea3ece2","tid":1609823,"uid":37054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"成日狗咬撚完人 ，亂拉完人你地剩係叫走啦黑狗<br />\n收隊啦黑狗<br />\n即係班狗咬撚完你亂拉完人，你就乜都唔做放佢走<br />\n佢知道咬完你乜事都冇，你會鼓勵佢安全撤退<br />\n下次咪更放心繼續咬你<br />\n應該叫佢地咪撚走呀死黑狗 屌你老母<br />\n當年打信長同lol，隊友比野怪咬完殘血，見佢唔夠打通常唔會比隻野狗同三狼咬死隊友再滿血返返原位，通常會一齊幫手打野怪<br />\n<br />\n信長火計石計清兵好快，石計cd短好好用<br />\n<br />\n利申：冷氣軍師"},{"pid":"58af12df275bff78444c922f85a72a42e864a03e","tid":1609823,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:35:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31bdd34e448730eb14e268297d962c7023f05697","tid":1609823,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:37:38.000Z","msg":"10月2號-HKDI罷課行動 請其他IVE院校借鑑<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/egixgS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/egixgS</a>"},{"pid":"7c7d2c6fad6f385b11b62f947777ba19076e0eef","tid":1609823,"uid":37054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:09:03.000Z","msg":"咁樣叫次次等佢地走，真係淨係會傷敵0，自損1000"},{"pid":"8be765f89163386ec3b1d463dc1d5f6701ddeba8","tid":1609823,"uid":37054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:18:21.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"036c48cd08aefcd8ef12ac9287d38304636d1cf2","tid":1609823,"uid":37054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:18:31.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"a3fcd3394e90ef6ca2ee2c78a719723c56b111d5","tid":1609823,"uid":37054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:18:41.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"d0e72b682bdc4cca4c5df4ce9372b7082a905493","tid":1609823,"uid":37054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB